milestones.description: Khaliq Dad and Hamid Hassan's 37-run partnership is AFG's highest for the 9th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 14 between Hamid Hassan and Hasti Gul
Asghar Afghan has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (7) for AFG, going past Mohammad Nabi
